ve found that hunting Frost Giants in Great Divide can be quite lucrative (but dangerous too). I started hunting these around 44 (though im only 45 now <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ), and did the first two Coldain Prayer Shawl Quests while getting good xp. It is quite gratifying to take down something of the size of a FG, but taking down four at once is even better. I use Bonds of Force, Circle of Force (Gravity Flux is overpriced in mana) and SoW potions (too lazy to do Jboots), and the best place to find them in my experience is near the Eastern Wastes zone. I use my SoTF to pull 4 giants and i deal with them with my spells. The only thing annoying about this is that in times when too many people are on, it becomes tough to find 4 giants to take, but when too few are on, it becomes tough to avoid them (in addition to the incredibly annoying Drakkel Wolves). The loot on the giants is good (1 - 5 plat, velium weapons), and you can sell the toes that drop for 30- 50 plat at times, though if you dont have a good shoulder item yet you'll want to save them and start the Prayer Shawl Quests. Killing the giants greatly affects your standing with the Coldain (I went from somewhere around dubious and apprehensive to amiably in a few hours), and it's great fun when you aren't in severe fear for your life. <br>
<br>
Rayner Runeshadow, Level 45 Wizard, Drinal Server <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=glinlor00>Glinlor00</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Site Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><br><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif><a href=mailto:glinlor@graffe.com style=text-decoration: none><font color=#FFFFFF>Contact Glinlor</font></a></font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 1446<br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/28/02 12:54 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Frost Giant Quadding</span><hr size=1> Shafli: Could you send me a email, glinlor@graffe.com<br>
