Minimum Level:29<br>
Maximum Level:35 (maybe 37)<br>
Zone Name: Marus Seru<br>
Camp Area/LOC: North Zone wall<br>
Mob List (HP): Stonegrabber (lvl 25-42), Weathered Stonegrabber (lvl 28-29), Crumbling Stonegrabber (lvl 25-2<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
Availability (1-&gt;10): 9 (nearly never camped)<br>
Loot Ranking (1-&gt;10): 2 (1-3pp, sometimes a boulder)<br>
Diff.Ranking (1-&gt;10): 7 (takes getting used to)<br>
Faction Affected: None<br>
<br>
Other Notes/Tips/Warnings: This is a great quadding spot, as it is nearly never camped. I suggest binding at the entrance to Mons Letalis in the tunnel for quick gate and agro clearing. SoTF (Staff of the Temperal Flux) is a great item to have here but this can be done without it. Sow  and  skin yourself   from the north wall run out and FLux or get the attention of a stonegrabber run him towards any others you see near by till you have four chasing you. circle them in large  circle  till you get them packed in then  BoF them. run on north wall from west to east or vise versa,turn and Cof them , very few if any mobs climb high enough on wall to add, rinse and repeat.<br>
Submitted by: Arekie<br>
